v1.3
====

  * Added effects when restoring a pearl
  * New configuration for costume messages
  * Mutable pearls: one item id for empty pearls and another for imbued pearls
	(can be the same and is configurable)
  * Better stack handling: pearls will stack properly when used
  
v1.2
====

  * Added effects when storing XP in a pearl
  * fix bug: XP bar and level visual doesn't update properly sometimes
  * Can use stacks of pearls
  * New messages colors!
  * Enabling use of items (like chests) when having a pearl in hand